{t:I LOVE YOU LORD #177}
{st:}

D CHORD

I love you Lord,
And I lift my voice,
To worship you,
Oh my soul, rejoice,
Take joy, my King,
In what you hear,
Let it be a sweet, sweet sound,
In your ear.

We love you, Lord,
And we lift our hearts,
To honor you,
Oh my soul, rejoice,
Take joy, our King,
In what you see,
Let it be a pleasing sight,
In your eyes.




